attributionInfo.brokerName: Compass RE Texas, LLC - The Woodlands

data.description: Welcome to sophistication and comfort in the prestigious gated section of Meadows at Imperial Oaks on a cul-de-sac lot in Conroe, Texas. This thoughtfully designed 5/6 bedroom, 4.5 bathroom, 3-car garage, J Patrick custom home boasts the perfect blend of form and function with gleaming hardwood flooring, elegant formal dining room with adjacent butler's pantry, sparkling quartz island kitchen open to the spacious living area, cozy fireplace, soaring ceilings, 2 bedrooms on the main level, dedicated home office, game room, comfortable media room, and secondary flex room on the second floor. Your new home comes complete with a covered patio with extended decking, spacious back and side yard, basketball court, and storage shed with electricity! Residents of Meadows at Imperial Oaks enjoy the benefits of a resort style swimming pool, splash pad, open air pavilion, community lakes, playgrounds, club house, and walking trails.
